1545
01:39:14,891 --> 01:39:15,892
12 giây, sir!

1546
01:39:16,017 --> 01:39:17,101
Phi hành đoàn the Enterprise,

1547
01:39:17,143 --> 01:39:18,603
Hãy chuẩn bị cho nổ.

